data.name: DBMS-Benchmarker
data.description: DBMS-Benchmarker is a Python-based application-level blackbox benchmark tool for Database Management Systems (DBMS). It connects to a given list of DBMS (via JDBC) and runs a given list of parametrized and randomized (SQL) benchmark queries. Evaluations are available via a Python interface and on an interactive multi-dimensional dashboard.

license.name: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
